{"tid":1563683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地就黎由上風比人扯翻落黎","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T22:57:36.000Z","uid":302248,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bca859df205e070669b0e033523a3609a8596d91","tid":1563683,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"大部分post唔係太子有冇做法事，就係講緊消防記者會。再係咁少行動post我地就玩完。<br />\n<br />\n所以！<br />\n<br />\n我地要繼續和理勇武結合，915仆出黎行街<br />\n<br />\n雖然今次嘅行動俾人發出反對通知書，但係我地可以借鑑以前用過嘅方法。包括宗教集會，握手會等。另外可以參照818金鐘夢境，以和理非主場，勇武其後介入，將呢場革命得以延續。<br />\n<br />\n香港呢場革命，係香港人嘅共業，我地要繼續加油，直至解放香港，達成五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n願榮光歸香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuZN0R4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuZN0R4.png&h=cad135f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb5addf361befa4c30f8831223ce62c1b4875c4f","tid":1563683,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c72b660b0682cce7d5fa71ddd082d1f55bac59","tid":1563683,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe4529ea567292939971c9fb49be06b1dab22a7","tid":1563683,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:18:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></di